&lt;h3 id=&#34;network-layers&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#network-layers&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Network Layers&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Application Level&lt;br /&gt;
(FTP, Telnet, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Transport Layer&lt;br /&gt;
(TCP, UDP, sockets, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Network Layer&lt;br /&gt;
(Low-level Protocol -- IP, datagrams, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hardware Layer&lt;br /&gt;
(Ethernet, TokenRing, X.25, etc.)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
