&lt;h3 id=&#34;networking-in-java&#34;&gt;&lt;a class=&#34;anchor&#34; href=&#34;#networking-in-java&#34;&gt;#&lt;/a&gt; Networking in Java&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The  &lt;code&gt;java.net&lt;/code&gt;  package contains classes and interfaces that provide a powerful infrastructure for networking in Java.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today, we see how networking in Java works.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We will check out the following: Load a document from the web&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Some packaged classes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
